WEBVTT

00:00:00.251 --> 00:00:03.432
Leading global enterprises introduces a unique challenge.

00:00:03.912 --> 00:00:08.013
The mechanics of trust and communication change drastically across borders.

00:00:08.613 --> 00:00:13.134
This brings up the critical competency of cultural intelligence, or CQ.

00:00:13.794 --> 00:00:18.695
CQ is a person's capability for successful adaptation to new cultural settings.

00:00:19.255 --> 00:00:28.117
While a global mindset allows for understanding the interdependence of the global economy, cultural intelligence focuses on the behavioral ability to interact

00:00:28.237 --> 00:00:31.098
interpersonally and bridge cultural differences.
